{% comment %}
  Free Gift Engine — cart app block.
  Phase 5b-1: loads the storefront controller (assets/free-gift.js) which wires the pure reconciler
  to the live AJAX cart (auto add/remove gift lines + apply the discount code). The perception UI
  (progress widget, "Choose your free gift" chooser, "Add my free gift" decline checkbox), polished
  styling, mobile, and a11y are Phase 5b-2.

  The widget NEVER sets prices (the minted code + Shopify discount do) and NEVER trusts client state
  for eligibility (the server recomputes in /validate).

  `default_choices` is a TEMPORARY 5b-1 seam: the OR/variant chooser UI is 5b-2, so for now the
  shopper's gift choice for OR tiers is a hardcoded default (JSON: { "<tierId>": "<optionId>" }).
{% endcomment %}

<div
  class="fge-app-block"
  data-fge-app-block
  data-proxy-path="/apps/free-gift/validate"
  data-presentment-currency="{{ cart.currency.iso_code }}"
  data-country="{{ localization.country.iso_code }}"
  data-default-choices="{{ block.settings.default_choices | escape }}"
  hidden
>
  {% comment %} 5b-2 renders the tier/progress widget, the gift chooser, and the decline checkbox here. {% endcomment %}
</div>

<script src="{{ 'free-gift.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Free Gift",
  "target": "section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "default_choices",
      "label": "Default gift choices (temporary, 5b-1)",
      "info": "JSON mapping tier id -> OR option id, e.g. {\"<tier1Id>\":\"a\"}. Replaced by the chooser UI in 5b-2.",
      "default": ""
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
